{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01KgXGtrseFyus1aDEZCaDeS","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01EugMM177cNwuzSyQFjnyNx","name":"Skill","input":{"skill":"para-memory-files","args":"Save feedback memory: Joeri expects agents to be proactive and autonomous. When an agent has no tasks but company goals exist, the agent should scan goals and create its own work ŌĆö not sit idle. \"Ik snap niet dat hier geen autonomy is\" was his exact frustration. Also update daily note for 2026-04-03 with JOEA-8 resolution: set up Sage workspace, created JOEA-9, closed JOEA-7 and JOEA-8."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":563,"cache_read_input_tokens":56131,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":563},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c6e79812-80c9-4ac3-a2b6-97965455eea2","uuid":"bf862154-071f-49c5-9d90-57409965435b"}
