-24): Rex content analysis workflow from Obsidian (Rex, depends on JOEA-23)\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Top Priorities This Week\\n\\n1. **[JOEA-19](/JOEA/issues/JOEA-19)** ŌĆö Fix agent errors on task resolution (Mitch) ŌĆö blocks team productivity\\n2. **[JOEA-11](/JOEA/issues/JOEA-11)** ŌĆö Complete news digest cron migration (Mitch, already in_progress)\\n3. **[JOEA-16](/JOEA/issues/JOEA-16) + [JOEA-17](/JOEA/issues/JOEA-17)** ŌĆö Joeri reviews content pillars + first LinkedIn post\\n4. **[JOEA-23](/JOEA/issues/JOEA-23)** ŌĆö Tommy designs Obsidian content pipeline\\n5. **[JOEA-14](/JOEA/issues/JOEA-14)** ŌĆö Daily AI news scanner for Webbio (Mitch, after queue reduces)\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Escalations / Decisions for Nox\\n\\n- **JOEA-16/17**: These require Joeri''s approval before Rex can publish. No agent can unblock this ŌĆö Joeri needs to review and approve the content pillars and first LinkedIn post draft.\"\n  }' | jq '{identifier: .identifier, status: .status}'","description":"Mark JOEA-20 done with weekly planning summary"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":590,"cache_read_input_tokens":40124,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":590},"output_tokens":41,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1b3e009e-3300-4d6b-a731-db949396751a","uuid":"2800a77b-fa76-4b65-9cf1-866009af7466"}
