{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01UG9hbFbGGk1AEcefCPqzSz","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01Q498T7e6eURTYCj7EthuaG","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"curl -s -X PATCH -H \"Authorization: Bearer $PAPERCLIP_API_KEY\" -H \"X-Paperclip-Run-Id: $PAPERCLIP_RUN_ID\" -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \"$PAPERCLIP_API_URL/api/issues/7445a5b8-24ed-47d3-b4b5-50151b3238af\" -d '{\n  \"status\": \"done\",\n  \"comment\": \"## Routines now live in Paperclip\\n\\nJe had gelijk ŌĆö instructies zonder taken betekent stilstaande agents. Opgelost.\\n\\n### Created this week'\\''s routine tasks\\n- [JOEA-20](/JOEA/issues/JOEA-20) ŌĆö **Sage**: Weekly planning (goal review, task inventory, priorities)\\n- [JOEA-21](/JOEA/issues/JOEA-21) ŌĆö **Oscar**: Weekly financial snapshot (bank data, buffer progress, cash flow)\\n- [JOEA-22](/JOEA/issues/JOEA-22) ŌĆö **Rex**: Weekly content cycle (trend scan ŌåÆ hooks ŌåÆ Joeri approval ŌåÆ publish)\\n\\nAll three are assigned and will trigger heartbeats. Sage, Oscar, and Rex will wake up and execute.\\n\\n### How the cycle sustains itself\\nSage'\\''s HEARTBEAT.md now includes the routine engine: every Monday she checks if routine tasks exist for the current week and creates them if missing. This means the cycle self-perpetuates ŌĆö I don'\\''t need to manually create them each week.\\n\\n### Daily involvement\\nSage runs a daily task health check on every heartbeat:\\n- Flags tasks in_progress >24h without updates\\n- Escalates unresolved blockers to me\\n- Redistributes if any agent is overloaded\\n\\nFriday wrap-up comes to me for strategic review before the next week kicks off.\"\n}' | python3 -m json.tool 2>/dev/null","description":"Close JOEA-18 with summary"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3897,"cache_read_input_tokens":70262,"cache_creation":{"