{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_014kQsR4cdgxbJfotKG4jY4A","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Obsidian Vault\n2\t\n3\tShared Obsidian vault at `~/.paperclip/instances/default/vault/` providing a human-readable window into all agent workspaces.\n4\t\n5\t## Key Details\n6\t\n7\t- Uses **real directories with file-level symlinks** (not directory symlinks) to link agent workspaces\n8\t- Directory symlinks don't work in Obsidian on macOS ŌĆö this was the root cause of folders appearing empty\n9\t- Sync script `.sync-vault.sh` in the vault root updates symlinks when agents create new files\n10\t- Agents: Mitch, Nox, Oscar, Rex, Tommy\n11\t- Dataview + Templater plugins configured but need manual install on first vault open\n12\t- Dashboards in `Dashboards/`, templates in `_templates/`\n13\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"441920ca-57e2-4d9f-8021-cbdca58bc1a4","uuid":"c343299a-c3a1-489f-b01d-0a694a09820e","timestamp":"2026-04-03T14:13:51.741Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/joerismits/.paperclip/instances/default/workspaces/467192bf-0ffd-49de-b18f-91a35b60e57a/life/projects/obsidian-vault/summary.md","content":"# Obsidian Vault\n\nShared Obsidian vault at `~/.paperclip/instances/default/vault/` providing a human-readable window into all agent workspaces.\n\n## Key Details\n\n- Uses **real directories with file-level symlinks** (not directory symlinks) to link agent workspaces\n- Directory symlinks don't work in Obsidian on macOS ŌĆö this was the root cause of folders appearing empty\n- Sync script `.sync-vault.sh` in the vault root updates symlinks when agents create new files\n- Agents: Mitch, Nox, Oscar, Rex, Tommy\n- Dataview + Templater plugins configured but need manual install on first vault open\n- Dashboards in `Dashboards/`, templates in `_templates/`\n","numLines":13,"startLine":1,"totalLines":13}}}
