ges (Agent Overview, People & Companies, Projects & Resources)\n  - Created 4 Templater templates (_templates/: Daily Note, Agent Note, Entity, Project)\n  - Configured .obsidian/ for Dataview + Templater community plugins\n- Updated Home.md with dashboard links\n- Marked JOEA-5 done\n\n## Heartbeat ~14:05 UTC\n\n- Woke via `issue_assigned` on JOEA-5 (reopened/reassigned)\n- User reported: agent folders visible in Obsidian sidebar but content not loading\n- Root cause: Obsidian on macOS doesn't follow directory-level symlinks properly\n- Fix: replaced all directory symlinks with real directories containing file-level symlinks\n  - Applied recursively through all agent workspace subdirs (life/, memory/, life/areas/, etc.)\n- Created `.sync-vault.sh` script in vault root for re-syncing when agents create new files\n- Created knowledge graph entity: `life/projects/obsidian-vault/`\n- Waiting for user to restart Obsidian and confirm fix works\n\n## Today's Plan\n- JOEA-5 in progress ŌĆö awaiting user confirmation that vault renders correctly in Obsidian.\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":38,"oldLines":5,"newStart":38,"newLines":12,"lines":[" - Created knowledge graph entity: `life/projects/obsidian-vault/`"," - Waiting for user to restart Obsidian and confirm fix works"," ","+## Heartbeat ~14:12 UTC","+","+- Woke via `issue_commented` ŌĆö user confirmed vault folders now visible in Obsidian","+- Fixed Dataview queries to exclude `_templates/` and `Dashboards/` folders (was showing template placeholders)","+- Added frontmatter to obsidian-vault project summary","+- Marked JOEA-5 done","+"," ## Today's Plan","-- JOEA-5 in progress ŌĆö awaiting user confirmation that vault renders correctly in Obsidian.","+- JOEA-5 done. Standing by for next assignment."]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
