{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01C7FTjBFdty3mGKszRBe63p","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01DwAqHijrzMZvMgES6uyznd","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/joerismits/.paperclip/instances/default/workspaces/467192bf-0ffd-49de-b18f-91a35b60e57a/memory/2026-04-03.md","old_string":"## Today's Plan\n- [x] JOEA-5: Obsidian vault optimization\n- [x] JOEA-10: Migrate Tempo hours cron (in_review, pending launchd install + gog re-auth)\n- [ ] JOEA-11: Migrate news digest cron\n- [ ] JOEA-14: Build daily AI news scanner\n- [ ] JOEA-15: Build weekly AI research digest\n- [ ] JOEA-12: Migrate films digest cron\n- [ ] JOEA-13: Migrate workspace sync cron","new_string":"## Heartbeat ~14:55 UTC\n\n- Woke via `issue_assigned` on JOEA-11 \"Migrate news digest cron to Paperclip\"\n- Reviewed OpenClaw implementation: daily at 08:30 CET, 6 RSS feeds (nu.nl x3, NOS, Tweakers, BBC), Claude Haiku curation, Discord channel 1478050132749455411\n- OpenClaw version had consecutive timeout errors (AI curation too slow within 180s)\n- Built `news-digest.py`: stdlib Python, rule-based curation (keyword scoring + category weighting), auto-truncation for Discord 2000 char limit\n- Created `news-config.json`, `run-news-cron.sh`, `nl.webbio.paperclip.news-cron.plist`\n- Tested: 102 items fetched from 6 feeds, 8 selected, posted to Discord successfully\n- Set JOEA-11 to `in_review`, reassigned to Tommy\n\n## Today's Plan\n- [x] JOEA-5: Obsidian vault optimization\n- [x] JOEA-10: Migrate Tempo hours cron (in_review, pending launchd install + gog re-auth)\n- [x] JOEA-11: Migrate news digest cron (in_review, pending launchd install)\n- [ ] JOEA-14: Build daily AI news scanner\n- [ ] JOEA-15: Build weekly AI research digest\n- [ ] JOEA-12: Migrate films digest cron\n- [ ] JOEA-13: Migrate workspace sync cron"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":320,"cache_read_input_tokens":57765,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":320},"output_tokens":65,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b7fe385b-bd33-447d-bb60-b8ee9aa829e9","uuid":"c2cc6272-af8b-4538-be6c-b91d8834436c"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01DwAqHijrzMZvMgES6uyznd","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /Users/joerismits/.paperclip/instances/default/workspaces/467192bf-0ffd-49de-b18f-91a35b60e57a/memory/2026-04-03.md has been updated successfully."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b7fe385b-bd33-447d-bb60-b8ee9aa829e9","uuid":"d3f70375-bbab-4606-af8a-ff01eb049ce3","timestamp":"2026-04-03T15:09:38.856Z","tool_use_result":{"filePath":"/Users/joerismits/.paperclip/instances/default/workspaces/467192bf-0ffd-49de-b18f-91a35b60e57a/memory/2026-04-03.md","oldString":"## Today's Plan\n- [x] JOEA-5: Obsidian vault optimization\n- [x] JOEA-10: Migrate Tempo hours cron (in_review, pending launchd install + gog re-auth)\n- [ ] JOEA-11: Migrate news digest cron\n- [ ] JOEA-14: Build daily AI news scanner\n- [ ] JOEA-15: Build weekly AI research digest\n- [ ] JOEA-12: Migrate films digest cron\n- [ ] JOEA-13: Migrate workspace sync cron","newString":"## Heartbeat ~14:55 UTC\n\n- Woke via `issue_assigned` on JOEA-11 \"Migrate news digest cron to Paperclip\"\n- Reviewed OpenClaw implementation: daily at 08:30 CET, 6 RSS feeds (nu.nl x3, NOS, Tweakers, BBC), Claude Haiku curation, Discord channel 1478050132749455411\n- OpenClaw version had consecutive timeout errors (AI curation too slow within 180s)\n- Built `news-digest.py`: stdlib Python, rule-based curation (keyword scoring + category weighting), auto-truncation for Discord 2000 char limit\n- Created `news-config.json`, `run-news-cron.sh`, `nl.webbio.paperclip.news-cron.plist`\n- Tested: 102 items fetched from 6 feeds, 8 selected, posted to Discord successfully\n- Set JOEA-11 to `in_review`, reassigned to Tommy\n\n## Today's Plan\n- [x] JOEA-5: Obsidian vault optimization\n- [x] JOEA-10: Migrate Tempo hours cron (in_review, pending launchd install + gog re-auth)\n- [x] JOEA-11: Migrate news digest cron (in_review, pending launchd install)\n- [ ] JOEA-14: Build daily AI news scanner\n- [ ] JOEA-15: Build weekly AI research digest\n- [ ] JOEA-12: Migrate films digest cron\n- [ ] JOEA-13: Migrate workspace sync cron","originalFile":"---\ntype: daily-note\nagent: Mitch\ndate: 2026-04-03\ntags: [daily]\n---\n\n# 2026-04-03 -- First Heartbeat\n\n## Identity\n- Agent: Mitch (CTO), id `467192bf-0ffd-49de-b18f-91a35b60e57a`\n- Company: `712f694b-097f-4ca4-b161-f299187ec27d`\n- Reports to: Nox (CEO, `23bc3620-04fa-40d0-8e4c-9a52ea800a9e`)\n- URL key: `mitch`\n\n## Timeline\n- **13:30 UTC** -- First heartbeat. No assignments in inbox. No wake trigger. PARA memory initialized. Exiting cleanly.\n\n## Heartbeat ~13:32 UTC\n\n- Woke via `issue_status_changed` on JOEA-5 \"Obsidian vault optimalisatie\"\n- Checked out and completed all 4 deliverables:\n  - Added YAML frontmatter (type/agent/tags/date) to 21 files across all agent workspaces\n  - Created 3 Dataview dashboard pages (Agent Overview, People & Companies, Projects & Resources)\n  - Created 4 Templater templates (_templates/: Daily Note, Agent Note, Entity, Project)\n  - Configured .obsidian/ for Dataview + Templater community plugins\n- Updated Home.md with dashboard links\n- Marked JOEA-5 done\n\n## Heartbeat ~14:05 UTC\n\n- Woke via `issue_assigned` on JOEA-5 (reopened/reassigned)\n- User reported: agent folders visible in Obsidian sidebar but content not loading\n- Root cause: Obsidian on macOS doesn't follow directory-level symlinks properly\n- Fix: replaced all directory symlinks with real directories containing file-level symlinks\n  - Applied recursively through all agent workspace subdirs (life/, memory/, life/areas/, etc.)\n- Created `.sync-vault.sh` script in vault root for re-syncing when agents create new files\n- Created knowledge graph entity: `life/projects/obsidian-vault/`\n- Waiting for user to restart Obsidian and confirm fix works\n\n## Heartbeat ~14:12 UTC\n\n- Woke via `issue_commented` ŌĆö user confirmed vault folders now visible in Obsidian\n- Fixed Dataview queries to exclude `_templates/` and `Dashboards/` folders (was showing template placeholders)\n- Added frontmatter to obsidian-vault project summary\n- Marked JOEA-5 done\n\n## Heartbeat ~14:17 UTC\n\n- Woke via `issue_reopened_via_comment` ŌĆö user frustrated, dashboards show no data\n- Root cause: Obsidian doesn't index ANY symlinks (file-level or directory-level)\n- Fix: replaced ALL symlinks with actual file copies using `cp`\n- Updated sync script to use `rsync` instead of `ln -s`\n- Lesson: Obsidian requires real files on disk, no symlinks at all\n- Not marking done until user confirms it works this time\n\n## Heartbeat ~14:20 UTC\n\n- Woke via `issue_commented` ŌĆö user still saw no data\n- Created Debug dashboard with 3 minimal Dataview tests\n- Removed `FROM` clause from all dashboards (possible syntax issue)\n- Asked user to switch to Reading View (Cmd+E)\n\n## Heartbeat ~14:24 UTC\n\n- User sent 3 screenshots of Debug dashboard ŌĆö **Dataview works!**\n- 34 files indexed, all entities/projects/daily-notes visible with correct frontmatter\n- Root cause was combination of: (1) symlinks not indexable, (2) user was in source editing mode\n- Changed default view to `preview` (reading mode) so Dataview renders by default\n- Cleaned up stale `0/` folder from old sync script bug\n- Marked JOEA-5 done ŌĆö confirmed working\n\n## Key Lessons (JOEA-5)\n\n1. Obsidian on macOS does NOT index symlinks ŌĆö need real file copies\n2. Dataview only renders in Reading View / Live Preview, not source editing mode\n3. `FROM -\"folder\"` syntax works but simpler `WHERE`-only queries are more reliable\n4. Always verify with user before marking done when UI is involved\n\n## Heartbeat ~14:47 UTC\n\n- Woke via `issue_assigned` on JOEA-10 \"Migrate Tempo hours logging cron to Paperclip\"\n- Found OpenClaw Tempo integration: `~/.openclaw/workspace/integrations/tempo-config.json` + `scripts/tempo-reconstruct.sh`\n- Script: Python-in-bash, fetches GitHub commits + Jira transitions + Google Calendar, produces JSON worklog drafts per Jira ticket\n- Migrated script + config to Paperclip project workspace, updated default paths\n- Tested: GitHub + Jira APIs work; `gog` OAuth token expired (calendar unavailable, pre-existing)\n- Created `run-tempo-cron.sh` wrapper and `nl.webbio.paperclip.tempo-cron.plist` for launchd\n- End-to-end test passed. Set JOEA-10 to `in_review`\n- Blocker for full parity: `gog auth` needed to restore calendar events\n\n## Today's Plan\n- [x] JOEA-5: Obsidian vault optimization\n- [x] JOEA-10: Migrate Tempo hours cron (in_review, pending launchd install + gog re-auth)\n- [ ] JOEA-11: Migrate news digest cron\n- [ ] JOEA-14: Build daily AI news scanner\n- [ ] JOEA-15: Build weekly AI research digest\n- [ ] JOEA-12: Migrate films digest cron\n- [ ] JOEA-13: Migrate workspace sync cron\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":88,"oldLines":10,"newStart":88,"newLines":20,"lines":[" - End-to-end test passed. Set JOEA-10 to `in_review`"," - Blocker for full parity: `gog auth` needed to restore calendar events"," ","+## Heartbeat ~14:55 UTC","+","+- Woke via `issue_assigned` on JOEA-11 \"Migrate news digest cron to Paperclip\"","+- Reviewed OpenClaw implementation: daily at 08:30 CET, 6 RSS feeds (nu.nl x3, NOS, Tweakers, BBC), Claude Haiku curation, Discord channel 1478050132749455411","+- OpenClaw version had consecutive timeout errors (AI curation too slow within 180s)","+- Built `news-digest.py`: stdlib Python, rule-based curation (keyword scoring + category weighting), auto-truncation for Discord 2000 char limit","+- Created `news-config.json`, `run-news-cron.sh`, `nl.webbio.paperclip.news-cron.plist`","+- Tested: 102 items fetched from 6 feeds, 8 selected, posted to Discord successfully","+- Set JOEA-11 to `in_review`, reassigned to Tommy","+"," ## Today's Plan"," - [x] JOEA-5: Obsidian vault optimization"," - [x] JOEA-10: Migrate Tempo hours cron (in_review, pending launchd install + gog re-auth)","-- [ ] JOEA-11: Migrate news digest cron","+- [x] JOEA-11: Migrate news digest cron (in_review, pending launchd install)"," - [ ] JOEA-14: Build daily AI news scanner"," - [ ] JOEA-15: Build weekly AI research digest"," - [ ] JOEA-12: Migrate films digest cron"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
