{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_018vgdiimz2YzHs4BsYq5Ra4","type":"tool_result","content":"{\n  \"issue\": {\n    \"id\": \"e67d3a6e-04cd-4ca0-beb3-42714853b49b\",\n    \"identifier\": \"JOEA-26\",\n    \"title\": \"Set up your Paperclip routines\",\n    \"description\": \"Create your recurring routine via the Paperclip routines API. Agents can only create routines assigned to themselves.\\n\\nUse `POST /api/companies/{companyId}/routines` with these fields:\\n- `projectId` (required, UUID)\\n- `title` (required)\\n- `description` (what to do when the routine fires)\\n- `assigneeAgentId` (your own agent ID)\\n- `cronExpression` (5-field cron, UTC)\\n- `priority`\\n- `goalId`\\n\\n**Create this routine:**\\n\\n1. **Weekly financial snapshot** ŌĆö Monday 07:00 UTC (09:00 CET)\\n   - `cronExpression`: `\\\"0 7 * * 1\\\"`\\n   - `projectId`: `\\\"2d1aac53-a8ad-4685-9db7-0fcf2e80fc4d\\\"` (Automation)\\n   - `goalId`: `\\\"a85d1f2d-bd31-46a0-b36a-022c0ebb9921\\\"`\\n   - Pull latest bank data via GoCardless/ING, categorize transactions, produce buffer progress, weekly cash flow, top expenses, trend vs last week, flag unusual items.\\n\\nMark this task done after the routine is created.\",\n    \"status\": \"todo\",\n    \"priority\": \"medium\",\n    \"projectId\": null,\n    \"goalId\": \"a85d1f2d-bd31-46a0-b36a-022c0ebb9921\",\n    \"parentId\": \"7445a5b8-24ed-47d3-b4b5-50151b3238af\",\n    \"assigneeAgentId\": \"d1e84034-4c31-4926-a145-8a1f713ba3fc\",\n    \"assigneeUserId\": null,\n    \"updatedAt\": \"2026-04-03T15:09:33.357Z\"\n  },\n  \"ancestors\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"7445a5b8-24ed-47d3-b4b5-50151b3238af\",\n      \"identifier\": \"JOEA-18\",\n      \"title\": \"Meer atonomy en feedback loops\",\n      \"status\": \"in_progress\",\n      \"priority\": \"critical\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"project\": null,\n  \"goal\": {\n    \"id\": \"a85d1f2d-bd31-46a0-b36a-022c0ebb9921\",\n    \"title\": \"joeri.dev is a personal company 