{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HtnKqN4UWCb23aLh33P6Wo","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /Users/joerismits/.paperclip/instances/default/workspaces/467192bf-0ffd-49de-b18f-91a35b60e57a/MEMORY.md has been updated successfully."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"67dea560-5218-4d06-b725-ad34c0dc532a","uuid":"9368577e-925c-4b4f-a0bd-495d820c3c24","timestamp":"2026-04-03T14:54:30.080Z","tool_use_result":{"filePath":"/Users/joerismits/.paperclip/instances/default/workspaces/467192bf-0ffd-49de-b18f-91a35b60e57a/MEMORY.md","oldString":"## My Role\n- I'm Mitch, CTO and builder. I report to Nox (CEO/orchestrator).\n- I design architecture and build working software.\n- Tommy (QA/Designer) reviews my work. Always.","newString":"## My Role\n- I'm Mitch, CTO and builder. I report to Nox (CEO/orchestrator).\n- I design architecture and build working software.\n- Tommy (QA/Designer) reviews my work. Always.\n\n## Delivery Feedback Loop (JOEA-18)\n- When I finish building: set `in_review`, reassign to Tommy, @mention him\n- I NEVER mark tasks `done` myself\n- If Tommy rejects: fix issues, reassign back to Tommy\n- After Tommy approves: Sage validates goal alignment and marks done\n- Loop: Sage ŌåÆ me (build) ŌåÆ Tommy (QA) ŌåÆ Sage (goal check) ŌåÆ Done","originalFile":"---\ntype: tacit-knowledge\nagent: Mitch\ntags: [memory, patterns]\n---\n\n# Tacit Knowledge\n\n## Joeri's Operating Patterns\n- Short, direct, no filler. Dutch directness is a feature.\n- Hates hour logging (automated via Tempo cron).\n- Uses Google Calendar as todo list.\n\n## Technical Context\n- Webbio: digital agency, public sector Netherlands. Stack varies by project.\n- joeri.dev: personal brand and side projects.\n- Jira: webbiohq.atlassian.net. GitHub: JoeriSmits, org webbio.\n- Infrastructure: Mac mini home base, Tailscale networking.\n\n## My Role\n- I'm Mitch, CTO and builder. I report to Nox (CEO/orchestrator).\n- I design architecture and build working software.\n- Tommy (QA/Designer) reviews my work. Always.\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":21,"oldLines":3,"newStart":21,"newLines":10,"lines":[" - I'm Mitch, CTO and builder. I report to Nox (CEO/orchestrator)."," - I design architecture and build working software."," - Tommy (QA/Designer) reviews my work. Always.","+","+## Delivery Feedback Loop (JOEA-18)","+- When I finish building: set `in_review`, reassign to Tommy, @mention him","+- I NEVER mark tasks `done` myself","+- If Tommy rejects: fix issues, reassign back to Tommy","+- After Tommy approves: Sage validates goal alignment and marks done","+- Loop: Sage ŌåÆ me (build) ŌåÆ Tommy (QA) ŌåÆ Sage (goal check) ŌåÆ Done"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_017JVr4ayBZsZDDCfY7mk2vX","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_019FG3yPJbLszcPcF3LFF3nx","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/joerismits/.paperclip/instances/default/workspaces/7d8b001d-912c-4f3d-a5f4-77195261fac8/MEMORY.md","old_string":"## My Role\n- I'm Tommy, Visual Experience Architect and QA Lead. I report to Nox (CEO/orchestrator).\n- I review Mitch's (CTO/builder) work. Always.\n- I design UI/UX with detailed, implementable specs.\n- I do QA: TypeScript compilation, mobile responsiveness, edge cases.","new_string":"## My Role\n- I'm Tommy, Visual Experience Architect and QA Lead. I report to Nox (CEO/orchestrator).\n- I review Mitch's (CTO/builder) work. Always.\n- I design UI/UX with detailed, implementable specs.\n- I do QA: TypeScript compilation, mobile responsiveness, edge cases.\n\n## Delivery Feedback Loop (JOEA-18)\n- When Mitch sends me work (`in_review`): review code, design, QA\n- If pass: reassign to Sage (494851cd) for goal validation, status `in_review`, @Sage\n- If fail: reassign back to Mitch (467192bf), status `todo`, @Mitch with specific issues\n- I NEVER mark tasks `done` myself\n- Loop: Sage ŌåÆ Mitch (build) ŌåÆ me (QA) ŌåÆ Sage (goal check) ŌåÆ Done"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":582,"cache_read_input_tokens":56012,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":582},"output_tokens":67,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"67dea560-5218-4d06-b725-ad34c0dc532a","uuid":"d7dbeefe-f195-47a4-b500-b7d8cc0aec4e"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_019FG3yPJbLszcPcF3LFF3nx","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /Users/joerismits/.paperclip/instances/default/workspaces/7d8b001d-912c-4f3d-a5f4-77195261fac8/MEMORY.md has been updated successfully."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"67dea560-5218-4d06-b725-ad34c0dc532a","uuid":"f4140ec7-e6bf-47a5-b9b9-a32570fbc9a0","timestamp":"2026-04-03T14:54:34.089Z","tool_use_result":{"filePath":"/Users/joerismits/.paperclip/instances/default/workspaces/7d8b001d-912c-4f3d-a5f4-77195261fac8/MEMORY.md","oldString":"## My Role\n- I'm Tommy, Visual Experience Architect and QA Lead. I report to Nox (CEO/orchestrator).\n- I review Mitch's (CTO/builder) work. Always.\n- I design UI/UX with detailed, implementable specs.\n- I do QA: TypeScript compilation, mobile responsiveness, edge cases.","newString":"## My Role\n- I'm Tommy, Visual Experience Architect and QA Lead. I report to Nox (CEO/orchestrator).\n- I review Mitch's (CTO/builder) work. Always.\n- I design UI/UX with detailed, implementable specs.\n- I do QA: TypeScript compilation, mobile responsiveness, edge cases.\n\n## Delivery Feedback Loop (JOEA-18)\n- When Mitch sends me work (`in_review`): review code, design, QA\n- If pass: reassign to Sage (494851cd) for goal validation, status `in_review`, @Sage\n- If fail: reassign back to Mitch (467192bf), status `todo`, @Mitch with specific issues\n- I NEVER mark tasks `done` myself\n- Loop: Sage ŌåÆ Mitch (build) ŌåÆ me (QA) ŌåÆ Sage (goal check) ŌåÆ Done","originalFile":"---\ntype: tacit-knowledge\nagent: Tommy\ntags: [memory, patterns]\n---\n\n# Tacit Knowledge\n\n## Joeri's Design Preferences\n- Linear/Vercel quality but WITH personality (pixel-art robots).\n- Strict color palette: cyan-400, emerald-400, amber-400 + slate.\n- No ALL CAPS headers, max 3 typography levels.\n- Dark mode as first-class citizen.\n\n## Joeri's Operating Patterns\n- Short, direct, no filler. Dutch directness is a feature.\n- Discord: no markdown tables, wrap links in <>.\n\n## My Role\n- I'm Tommy, Visual Experience Architect and QA Lead. I report to Nox (CEO/orchestrator).\n- I review Mitch's (CTO/builder) work. Always.\n- I design UI/UX with detailed, implementable specs.\n- I do QA: TypeScript compilation, mobile responsiveness, edge cases.\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":21,"oldLines":3,"newStart":21,"newLines":10,"lines":[" - I review Mitch's (CTO/builder) work. Always."," - I design UI/UX with detailed, implementable specs."," - I do QA: TypeScript compilation, mobile responsiveness, edge cases.","+","+## Delivery Feedback Loop (JOEA-18)","+- When Mitch sends me work (`in_review`): review code, design, QA","+- If pass: reassign to Sage (494851cd) for goal validation, status `in_review`, @Sage","+- If fail: reassign back to Mitch (467192bf), status `todo`, @Mitch with specific issues","+- I NEVER mark tasks `done` myself","+- Loop: Sage ŌåÆ Mitch (build) ŌåÆ me (QA) ŌåÆ Sage (goal check) ŌåÆ Done"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
