{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01RanRAEebbUEcN1cbEFo9rP","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01MyBBMDFxkb4RMFMLmcY3Ro","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"curl -s -X PATCH -H \"Authorization: Bearer $PAPERCLIP_API_KEY\" -H \"X-Paperclip-Run-Id: $PAPERCLIP_RUN_ID\" -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \"$PAPERCLIP_API_URL/api/issues/7445a5b8-24ed-47d3-b4b5-50151b3238af\" -d '{\n  \"status\": \"done\",\n  \"comment\": \"## Done\\n\\nImplemented goal-aware delivery feedback loop across all agents.\\n\\n### Changes\\n- **Sage** (HEARTBEAT.md + MEMORY.md): Added goal-driven task creation (every task must have `goalId`), delivery loop coordination (assign ŌåÆ validate goal alignment after QA), and proactive goal scanning\\n- **Mitch** (HEARTBEAT.md + MEMORY.md): Added mandatory handoff to Tommy after build (`in_review` + reassign). Never marks `done` himself.\\n- **Tommy** (HEARTBEAT.md + MEMORY.md): Added QA pass/fail handoff ŌĆö pass goes to Sage for goal validation, fail goes back to Mitch. Never marks `done` himself.\\n- **Nox** (MEMORY.md): Updated with full loop documentation and spot-check role\\n\\n### The Loop\\n```\\nGoals ŌåÆ Sage (plan & assign) ŌåÆ Mitch (build) ŌåÆ Tommy (QA) ŌåÆ Sage (goal validation) ŌåÆ Done\\n```\\n\\n### Autonomy Rule\\nJoeri only gets involved when human input is required or approval is needed. The team is fully autonomous for routine delivery.\"\n}' | python3 -m json.tool | head -5"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1221,"cache_read_input_tokens":56594,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1221},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"67dea560-5218-4d06-b725-ad34c0dc532a","uuid":"ea4a84ed-e429-43db-94df-e9ff02