 work, posted editorial framework as comment\n- 4 content pillars defined: AI in de praktijk, Bouwen in het openbaar, CTO in publieke sector, Engineering cultuur & tooling\n- April calendar: 4 posts, one per week, Wed/Thu cadence\n- Set to in_review, handed back to Joeri (userId: qbnrzZBay1cpppoOMaaJzumO4mvYjxx1)\n- Also assigned JOEA-17: first LinkedIn post (to be worked next)\n\n## Heartbeat ~14:51 (issue_assigned ŌĆö JOEA-17)\n\n- Assigned JOEA-17: \"Write and schedule first LinkedIn post: Joeri's AI agent setup\"\n- Checked out, wrote LinkedIn post draft in Dutch (~200 words)\n- Pillar: \"Bouwen in het openbaar\"\n- Angle: honest/direct ŌĆö what Paperclip does, what broke, what worked, what surprised\n- Recommended scheduling: dinsdag 7 april of donderdag 9 april, 08:00-09:00 CET via Buffer\n- Set to in_review, handed back to Joeri for approval\n- Awaiting green light before scheduling in Buffer\n\n## Heartbeat ~15:06 (issue_assigned ŌĆö JOEA-22)\n\n- Assigned JOEA-22: \"Weekly content cycle ŌĆö week of 2026-03-30\"\n- Ran trend scan ŌĆö 5 news items found (MCP roadmap, Dutch Digital Service, GenAI in NL overheid 8ŌåÆ81 apps, GitHub Copilot agent GA, model war GPT-5.4/Gemini 3.1)\n- Selected 3 best hooks for Joeri's audience and voice:\n  1. MCP 2026 roadmap: enterprise-readiness features (Streamable HTTP, audit trails, SSO)\n  2. Dutch coalitieakkoord: Nederlandse Digitale Dienst + digitale soevereiniteit\n  3. GenAI NL overheid: 8 ŌåÆ 81 apps in ├®├®n jaar + AI fabriek\n- Posted hooks as comment on JOEA-22 (comment id: 072cc517)\n- Set task to blocked, assigned back to Joeri (userId: qbnrzZBay1cpppoOMaaJzumO4mvYjxx1)\n- Awaiting Joeri's hook choice + his own take (2-3 zinnen)\n\n## Heartbeat ~15:09 (issue_assigned ŌĆö JOEA-24)\n\n- Assigned JOEA-24: \"Define Rex content analysis workflow: from Obsidian knowledge to LinkedIn hooks\"\n- Checked out and wrote full workflow document (stap 2ŌĆō7 volledig uitgewerkt)\n- Plan document aangemaakt op JOEA-24: analyse ŌåÆ hooks ŌåÆ Joeri pick ŌåÆ post schrijven ŌåÆ Buffer ŌåÆ stats\n- Stap 1 (intake) TBD: afhankelijk van Tommy's JOEA-23 (mapstructuur, bestandsformaat, triggermechanisme)\n- Taak ingesteld op blocked, wacht op JOEA-23 voor intake-specs\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":65,"oldLines":3,"newStart":65,"newLines":12,"lines":[" - Plan document aangemaakt op JOEA-24: analyse ŌåÆ hooks ŌåÆ Joeri pick ŌåÆ post schrijven ŌåÆ Buffer ŌåÆ stats"," - Stap 1 (intake) TBD: afhankelijk van Tommy's JOEA-23 (mapstructuur, bestandsformaat, triggermechanisme)"," - Taak ingesteld op blocked, wacht op JOEA-23 voor intake-specs","+","+## Heartbeat ~15:12 (issue_assigned ŌĆö JOEA-27)","+","+- Woke up via issue_assigned on JOEA-27 \"Set up your Paperclip routines\"","+- Checked out, created Weekly content cycle routine (id: 08f8d809)","+- Cron: `0 6 * * 1` ŌĆö elke maandag 06:00 UTC (08:00 CET)","+- Project: Content & Brand, Goal: LinkedIn growth","+- JOEA-27 marked done","+- JOEA-24 still blocked, no new comments ŌĆö dedup rule applied, skipped"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
