{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_014NBpMVaR4hatCwhsFC5A8t","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01CP2FmULAFVXCdvaMuYii6N","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"curl -s -X PATCH -H \"Authorization: Bearer $PAPERCLIP_API_KEY\" -H \"X-Paperclip-Run-Id: $PAPERCLIP_RUN_ID\" -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \"$PAPERCLIP_API_URL/api/issues/7445a5b8-24ed-47d3-b4b5-50151b3238af\" -d '{\n  \"status\": \"in_progress\",\n  \"comment\": \"## Routines now in Paperclip\\n\\nJe keek naar [/JOEA/routines](/JOEA/routines) ŌĆö terecht. Ik had de instructies geschreven maar niet de Paperclip routines API gebruikt.\\n\\n### Created (live on /JOEA/routines)\\n- **Weekly goal review** ŌĆö Nox, vrijdag 17:00 CET\\n- **Daily operations check** ŌĆö Nox, werkdagen 11:00 CET\\n\\n### Delegated (agents moeten eigen routines aanmaken)\\nAgents kunnen alleen routines voor zichzelf maken. Taken aangemaakt:\\n- [JOEA-25](/JOEA/issues/JOEA-25) ŌĆö **Sage**: weekly planning (ma) + weekly wrap-up (vr)\\n- [JOEA-26](/JOEA/issues/JOEA-26) ŌĆö **Oscar**: weekly financial snapshot (ma)\\n- [JOEA-27](/JOEA/issues/JOEA-27) ŌĆö **Rex**: weekly content cycle (ma)\\n\\nZodra zij hun routines aanmaken verschijnen die ook op /JOEA/routines. Ik houd dit open tot alles staat.\"\n}' | python3 -m json.tool 2>/dev/null | grep '\"status\"'","description":"Update JOEA-18 with progress"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":377,"cache_read_input_tokens":92623,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":377},"output_tokens":67,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8562baa3-58e2-42cb-ab9d-4fa13b8c7a66","uuid":"a514c8ca-e138-48e2-b2ac-f6256be41ebe"}
