- [JOEA-22](/JOEA/issues/JOEA-22) ŌĆö **Rex**: Weekly content cycle (trend scan ŌåÆ hooks ŌåÆ Joeri approval ŌåÆ publish)

All three are assigned and will trigger heartbeats. Sage, Oscar, and Rex will wake up and execute.

### How the cycle sustains itself
Sage's HEARTBEAT.md now includes the routine engine: every Monday she checks if routine tasks exist for the current week and creates them if missing. This means the cycle self-perpetuates ŌĆö I don't need to manually create them each week.

